{
  "texts": [
    "The number of instructions in these datasets is all within 1K, with some limitations in comprehensiveness.",
    "SuperCLUE(Xu et al, 2023e)",
    "expands the scale of evaluation content.",
    "It serves as a comprehensive evaluation benchmark for Chinese general LLMs, designed to assess the effectiveness of current Chinese LLMs.",
    "The tasks include multiturn open-ended Q&A and objective multiple-choice Q&A, with monthly updates and significant reference value."
  ]
}